  <section id="about" class="section-padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
          <h2 class="ser-title">Since 1942</h2>
          <hr class="botm-line">
          <p>The Beta Kappa chapter of Lambda Chi Alpha was established in 1942, but has much deeper roots within the Georgia Tech community.
            <br>
            <br>
            Established with the purpose of recruiting the finest gentlemen and guiding them on their journey through university, Beta Kappa has evolved into the premier fraternity on campus, providing a Lifetime of Brotherhood to over 2000 gentlemen. If you'd like to learn about the 75 years of history in the Beta Kappa chapter, click
            <a href="#"> here</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-2 col-sm-6">
          <img src="../img/82Wreck.jpg" class="img-responsive img-rounded"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section id="service" class="section-padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-md-offset-1 col-md-push-6">
          <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="head-title lg-line">Service and Stewardship</h2>
            <hr class="botm-line">
            <p class="sec-para">Every year Lambda Chi Alpha collects hundreds of thousands of pounds of cans for Feeding America. As a national fraternity, we have raised over 10 million pounds since 2013. Within our local chapter, we participate in the annual St. Baldricks competition which benefits childhood cancer research. To find out more about our philanthropy, click
            <a href="#"> here</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-2 col-sm-6 col-md-pull-7">
          <img src="../img/baldricks.jpg" class="img-responsive img-rounded"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section id="scholarship" class="section-padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
          <h2 class="ser-title">Scholarship</h2>
          <hr class="botm-line">
          <p class="sec-para">Lambda Chi Alpha provides multiple scholarships ranging anywhere up to $2000 for incoming gentlemen.
            <br>
            <br>
            Check out the Beta Kappa Scholarship for incoming gentlemen
            <a href="#"> here</a>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-2 col-sm-6">
            <img src="../img/freshman.jpg" class="img-responsive img-rounded"/>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
